Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当你降临于这尘世时\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}As you come into this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}某样事物随之而生\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}something else is also born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你开启你的人生 它踏上它的征程\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You begin your life, and it begins a journey…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向你进发\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它缓步而行 但从不停止\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It moves slowly, but it never stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论你去哪 选择哪条路\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Wherever you go, whatever path you take,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它都步步相随\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}it will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不疾不徐 总是向你走来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Never faster, never slower, always coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会大步奔跑\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You will run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它则悠悠漫步\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It will walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会停下休息\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You will rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它则不会\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}某天 你会在某个地方流连太久\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}One day, you will linger in the same place too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你坐得太稳 或睡得太沉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You will sit too still or sleep too deep…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}直到很晚 你才起身离去\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And when, too late, you rise to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会注意到身旁出现另一个身影\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You will notice a second shadow next to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的生命在此终结\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Your life will then be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你以为她的死会使我变得脆弱\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If you think because she is dead, I am weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你对我知之甚少\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}then you understand very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你与她的死亡有关 而毫无惧意\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If you were any part of killing her, and you're not afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你就是个一无所知的蠢货\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}then you understand nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以奉劝你一句 听好了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, for your own sake, understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是博士\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I am the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来找你了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm coming to find you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我永远不会停止\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and I will never, ever stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(193.8,150,196.2,175.2)}{\fnSimHei\fsp2\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H030101&\fs12\t(\fs34}神秘博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(196.2,175.2,196.2,180.2)}{\fnSimHei\fsp2\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HFFFFFF&\fs34\t(\fs35)}神秘博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(196.2,180.2,198.6,196.4)}{\fnSimHei\fsp2\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HFFFFFF&\fs35\t(\fs48}神秘博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\move(193,185,193,215)\fnSimHei\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\t(\fs26)}天堂来使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那间屋子里的设备类似于\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The equipment in that room is consistent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}某种增强版超远程传送装置\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}with an augmented ultra long-range teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我距离出发地不超过一光年\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, I'm not more than a single light year from where I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且还在同一时区\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and I'm in the same time zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当太阳下山时\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}When the sun sets,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可以通过群星推算出准确的方位\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'll be able to establish an exact position by the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到时候你可有的选了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Then you'll have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现身 露出你的真面目\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Come out, show yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或者继续躲藏\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}or keep on hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉拉说了 不要我复仇\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Clara said I shouldn't take revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要知道 我有时候不太听话\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You should know, I don't always listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是园丁吗 我讨厌园艺\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Well, are you gardeners? I hate gardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么样的人才会有支配花朵的情结\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}What sort of a person has a power complex about flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是弱者的独裁方式\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's dictatorship for inadequates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或者换句话说 这就是独裁\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Or to put it another way, it's dictatorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来吧 快点\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Come on! Chop, chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}博士现在就要见你\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The Doctor will see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我看看你有什么能耐\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Show me what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我刚目睹了至亲好友痛苦离世\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I just watched my best friend die in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的日子不能更糟了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}My day can't get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我们看看能拿你的小日子怎么办\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Let's see what we can do about yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我认识你\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以前见过你\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I've seen you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我年轻时会玩心灵感应 有个小技巧\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I used to know a trick, back when I was young and telepathic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}显然 你不能跟门建立心灵连接\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Clearly, you can't make an actual psychic link with a door,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原因很明显\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}for one very obvious reason
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它们怒火中烧\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}they're notoriously cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想想 作为门的一生 净被人推着过了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I mean, imagine life as a door. People keep pushing past you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家总是在敲门 却从不是找你\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}All of that knocking, but it's never for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且每晚都会被锁住\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And you get locked up every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你能有一点点的善意\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}so if you're just a little bit nice…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看到没 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}See, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宝刀未老\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Still got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我…\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我实在找不到出路了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can't actually see a way out of this…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我终于无路可逃了 我的一生到此为止\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I've finally run out of corridor. There's a life summed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这倒新鲜 我害怕了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Now, this is new. I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才意识到 我真的害怕死亡\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I just realised that I'm actually scared of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说了什么吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Something I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我刚说了什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么停下了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很老 非常老\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Old. Very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}极有可能非常非常古老了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Possibly very, very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当我还是个小男孩时 有位老妇人过世了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}When I was a very little boy, there was an old lady who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们用纱布将她盖住\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}They covered her in veils,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但天气实在太热了 于是招来了苍蝇\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}but it was a hot, sunny day, and the flies came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一幕造就了我数年的噩梦\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It gave me nightmares for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 谁把我的噩梦放在了这里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, who's been stealing my nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么把我放在这里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}What am I here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一定认识我很久了 对吧\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You've known about me for a very long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 这是什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一个陷阱吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is it a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一座监狱吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is it a prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是一间拷问室吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is it a torture chamber?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说的对吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}某人真应该再多了解一下\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Somebody really should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}任何可以建造这里 又能偷走我噩梦的人\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Anyone who can put all of this together and steal my bad dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们应该更清楚\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}they should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的那些秘密 没门\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The secrets I have - no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不会说的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}No telling, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我跟你说了我很怕死 我也没说谎\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I told you I was scared of dying. And I wasn't lying either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}优势就是 我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Advantage - me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你绝对料不到下面这招\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Because you won't see THIS coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 我迟到了 跳了个窗子\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Sorry, I'm late! Jumped out of a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死定了 你想知道我怎么逃脱的吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Certain death. Don't you want to know how I survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来啊 问我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Go on. Ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}错 我当然必须要跳\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}No, of course I had to jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在被审讯时 第一条原则就是\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The first rule of being interrogated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是拷问室里唯一不可替代的人\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}is that you are the only irreplaceable person in the torture chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里是你的地盘 所以你做主\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The room is yours, so work it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果他们用死亡威胁你\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If they're going to threaten you with death,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就让他们看看谁才是老大\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}show them who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先死一步\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Die faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你比大多数人更常看见我这么做\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You've seen me do that more often than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吧 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Isn't that right, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死亡规则第一条 别死\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Rule one of dying - don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第二条 放慢速度\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Rule two - slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的生命掌握在自己手中\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You've got the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想得越快 它就会走得越慢\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The faster you think, the slower it will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}集中精力\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想着你会活下来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Assume you're going to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远都这么想\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Always assume that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想象你已经活了下来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Imagine you've already survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在你的脑海里有一个避难间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}There's a storm room in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}锁上门好好思考\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Lock the door and think!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是我的避难间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}This is my storm room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我总是想象着回到塔迪斯\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I always imagine that I'm back in my Tardis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向你炫耀\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}showing off,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉你我如何逃出生天 让你放声大笑\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}telling you how I escaped, making you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我现在就在这么做\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's what I'm doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正在坠落 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I am falling, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我濒临死亡\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后我要向你解释 我是如何活下来的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And I'm going to explain to you how I survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等不及要听听我说了什么了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can't wait to hear what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有听众我什么都不是\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm nothing without an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一线希望 盐\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}One hope - salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之前好像闻到过\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Thought I smelled it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打破窗户后我就确信了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}When I broke the window, I was sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}带咸味的空气 这座城堡是立于海中的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Salty air. This castle is standing in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从高处直接落入水中\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Diving into water from a great height
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不一定能够活下来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}is no guarantee of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我需要知道准确的跌落距离和速度\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I need to know exactly how far I'm going to fall, and how fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道我为何扔了板凳吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Why do you think I threw the stool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}估算落水时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Fall time to impact…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}七秒钟\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}'Seven seconds.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你料不到下面这招\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Because you won't see this coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}板凳的风阻\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The wind resistance of the stool,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大气的密度\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}the atmospheric density…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本地重力场的强度\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The strength of the local gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是不是拆穿了魔术把戏\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Am I spoiling the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就是干这个的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I work at this stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}距离接触水面还有\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Should hit the water in about…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}0.02秒\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}0.02 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保持意识清醒的几率为\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The chances of remaining conscious are…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fad(500,0)}问题一 这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能睡下去吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Can't I just sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}问题二 你说了什么让那个生物停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我非要什么都知道吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Do I have to know everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}你怎样才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉拉 我不能每次都…\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Clara, I can't always…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}赢？？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它一直跟着我 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It keeps coming, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去哪里它都跟着 为什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Wherever I go, it follows. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它为什么这样做\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Why does it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}问错了问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是老师 那正确的问题是什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Always the teacher. What's the right question, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}不是为何\N而是如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它在跟着我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去哪里 它都在追踪我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Wherever I go, it's tracking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}步履缓慢 打着吓人的趔趄\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Slowly though. Scary lurching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓人\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些无处不在的屏幕\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}These screens everywhere…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}时时刻刻告诉我它在哪里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's showing me exactly where it is all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它到哪里了 离我多近\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}how far it's got, how near.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为它是在故意吓我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Because it's trying to scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在我耳边呼吸的音效\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Putting its breath on my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是目的 这就是它的行为\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's the point! That's what it's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是个剧院\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}This is theatre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全是为了制造恐惧\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's all about fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}合理假设\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Working hypothesis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正处于一个全自动鬼屋 一个机械迷宫\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm in a fully automated haunted house. A mechanical maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是一个以吓死我为目标的致命迷箱\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's a killer puzzle box designed to scare me to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我正被困其中\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and I'm trapped inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}简直是我的圣诞节\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Must be Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又一把铲子\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Another spade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有人想要我挖地\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Someone wants me to dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉拉 你怎么看\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}What do you think, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有人在给我提示吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is someone trying to give me a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会怎么做\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 没错 你当然会这样\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Yes. Yes, of course you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说白了 这也正是你的死因\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Which, let's be honest, is what killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有人在试图告诉我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}someone is trying to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个花园里埋着重要的东西\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}that there's something important buried in this garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这基本上是它们告诉我的第一件事\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's almost the first thing they tried to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可能是个诡计\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Could be a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也可能是前人留下的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Could be one of my predecessors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我不是这里的第一个囚徒 对吧\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Because I'm not the first prisoner here, am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所有那些头骨\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}All those skulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道他们哪一步走错了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Wonder where they all went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么高的建筑\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Building this height,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么缓慢的生物 然后呢\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}creature that slow, so what…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一小时\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}An hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三角形力学 你输了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Physics of a triangle. You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以呢\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它会设置陷阱 没关系\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It can set traps. That's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我对陷阱最在行了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm good at traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你现在要去哪儿呢\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, where are you off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里只有唯一的出入口\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Only one way in and one way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然你走了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Well, seeing as you're going…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不 这不对\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}No, no. That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}我在第十二号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.73,0:24:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才又差一点\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Well, that was another close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或者说很有可能\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Or it would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我最后总会虎口脱险\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}once I've been and gone and got myself out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这回我是怎么做到的呢\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, how am I going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来吧 老师 问我问题\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Come on, teacher, ask me questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}别说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的害怕死亡\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm actually scared of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}问题二 你说了什么让那个生物停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真相 没错\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The truth, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但不是什么随便的真相 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But not any old truth, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个地方就是为了吓我而设计的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}This whole place is designed to terrify me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正在被审问\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm being interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.03,0:24:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它想要的不只是真相 那不够\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's not just truth it wants. That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.79,0:24:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是忏悔\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.21,0:24:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须说出我从没说过的真相\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I have to tell truths I've never told before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.25,0:24:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是唯一能阻止它的办法\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's the only thing that stops it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.41,0:24:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 问题是\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You see, the problem is…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.67,0:24:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Clara…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有些真相我永远不能说出口\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}There are truths that I can never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.55,0:25:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论如何都不行\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Not for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.59,0:25:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我现在又害怕又孤单\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But I'm scared and I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.06,0:25:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孤单\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.02,0:25:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且非常非常害怕\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And very, very scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.56,0:25:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我忏悔\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.36,0:25:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我离开伽里弗雷不是因为无聊\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I didn't leave Gallifrey because I was bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.28,0:25:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是谎话 一直都是谎话\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That was a lie! It's always been a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.68,0:25:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不够吗 你还想要更多\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Not enough? You want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我害怕 我逃跑是因为我害怕\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I was scared! I ran because I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.07,0:25:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是你想让我说的吗 这足够真实了吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is that what you want me to say? Is that true enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.21,0:27:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奇怪的是\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.53,0:27:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你失去某人的那天不是最糟的日子\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}the day you lose someone isn't the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少你还有事可做\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}At least you've got something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.16,0:27:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最糟的是他们死后不再回来的日子\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's all the days they stay dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.85,0:27:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}五十七分钟\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}57 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.87,0:27:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的世界就是这样运转的 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}This is how my world works, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.50,0:27:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一秒一秒数着流逝的时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I tick off the seconds as they pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.26,0:27:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的生命就是一场倒计时\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}My life is a countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.08,0:27:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我把这个生物引到城堡的一端\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If I draw the creature to one extreme of the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.04,0:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后我自己跑向另一端\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and I run to the other extreme,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.55,0:27:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我最多可以为自己争取到\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can earn myself a maximum
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.74,0:27:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}八十二分钟\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}of 82 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.02,0:27:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有八十二分钟\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}82 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.49,0:27:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用来吃饭 睡觉 工作\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}to eat, sleep and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.64,0:28:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的工作是寻找十二号房间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}My work is finding Room 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.59,0:28:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个城堡想要我这么做 它在引诱我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The castle wants me to. It's luring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.04,0:28:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}数字排列有些混乱\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The numbering is a bit confused,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.83,0:28:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}似乎所有房间编号都被打乱了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}as if the rooms are all jumbled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.01,0:28:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可能它们会移动\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Maybe they move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能看见整个城堡的移动\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I saw the whole castle move…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.47,0:28:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在我让那生物停下之时\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}When I made the creature stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.85,0:28:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每个房间 如果我离开足够长的时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Every room, if I leave it long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.06,0:28:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就会回到我刚到来时的状态\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}reverts to its condition at the moment I arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.42,0:28:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它会自我清理\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It tidies up after itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.68,0:28:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像全自动家政服务\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Automated room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.67,0:28:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我认为这整个地方处于一个闭合能量环里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I think this whole place is inside a closed energy loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.64,0:28:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无限循环\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}constantly recycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.70,0:29:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或者说我在地狱里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Or maybe I'm in Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.82,0:29:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没关系 我不怕地狱\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's OK. I'm not scared of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.64,0:29:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那只不过是坏人的天堂\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's just Heaven for bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.09,0:29:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我还要在这里待多久\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But how long will I have to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.79,0:29:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.81,0:29:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它一直跟着我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's always coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.90,0:29:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}越来越近\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Always closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倒计时永远不会停止\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The countdown never stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.91,0:29:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但倒计时的终点是什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But the countdown to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每个人的生命中都有两件大事无人记得\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}There are two events in everybody's life that nobody remembers,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两件所有生物都会经历的大事\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}two moments experienced by every living thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.21,0:29:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 却无人记得其中点滴\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Yet, no-one remembers anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.12,0:30:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有人记得自己的出生\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Nobody remembers being born…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.07,0:30:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也没有人记得自己的死亡\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and nobody remembers dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.22,0:30:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我们才会盯着头骨的眼眶\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is that why we always stare into the eye sockets of a skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我们在问\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Because we're asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.08,0:30:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什么感觉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"What was it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.38,0:30:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}疼吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.38,0:30:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还在害怕吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"Are you still scared?"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.16,0:30:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}鸟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.86,0:30:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鸟儿 这跟鸟儿有什么关系\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"Bird"? What's "Bird" got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.63,0:30:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里有鸟儿吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Are there birds here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.42,0:31:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我漏掉了什么 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}There's something I'm missing, Clara,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.88,0:31:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我觉得是非常可怕的事情\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and I think it's something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.01,0:31:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有人吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.92,0:31:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 有人在里边吗 有人吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Hello, is there someone there? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.64,0:32:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是个陷阱 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's a trap, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.60,0:32:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诱饵和陷阱\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}A lure and a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.26,0:32:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我跟随着为我洒下的面包屑\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm following breadcrumbs laid out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.50,0:32:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是某人的游戏\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}This is somebody's game…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我身不由己\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And I can't stop playing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.63,0:32:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所有来过的人都输了的游戏\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}a game everybody else has lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.10,0:32:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道怎么移动那些墙 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I know how to move that wall, Clara,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.51,0:32:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要我不停的忏悔\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}so long as I don't run out of confessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.46,0:32:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我真正想知道的是…\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But what I really want to know is…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.65,0:32:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是谁摆弄了天上的星星\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Who's been playing about with the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.32,0:32:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它们的位置都错了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}They're all in the wrong places,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.79,0:32:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少对于这个时区来说\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}for this time zone, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.77,0:32:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很清楚我没有穿越时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I know I didn't time travel to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.06,0:32:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能感知时间旅行\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can Fell time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.89,0:33:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我不知道\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If I didn't know better,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.16,0:33:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会以为自己穿越到了七千年后的未来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'd say I've travelled 7,000 years into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.86,0:33:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我十分清楚没有\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But I do know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.57,0:33:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以是谁移动了星辰的位置\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, who moved the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.07,0:33:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混血\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The Hybrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.25,0:33:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}远在时间大战之前\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Long before the Time War,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.94,0:33:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}时间领主就知道它会到来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}the Time Lords knew it was coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.22,0:33:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像来临的风暴\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}like a storm on the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.77,0:33:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有许多预言和故事\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}There were many prophecies and stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.06,0:33:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事情发生之前就有了传说\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}legends before the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.16,0:33:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其中之一就是关于"混血"这种生物\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}One of them was about a creature called the Hybrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.63,0:33:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}半戴立克 半时间领主\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Half Dalek, half Time Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.20,0:33:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终极战士\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The ultimate warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.13,0:33:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但它会站在哪一边\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But whose side would it be on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.01,0:33:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它会带来和平还是毁灭\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Would it bring peace or destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它真实存在 还是无端的幻想\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Was it real, or a fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.81,0:33:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我忏悔\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I confess,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.90,0:33:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道"混血"真实存在\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I know the Hybrid is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.47,0:34:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道它在哪里 它是什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I know where it is, and what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.22,0:34:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我忏悔 我很害怕\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I confess, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.88,0:35:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8\fad(0,500)}家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.50,0:35:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.27,0:35:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最后一片拼图\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The last square on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.80,0:35:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不然还能是什么呢\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}What else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.36,0:35:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}塔迪斯\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The Tardis.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.53,0:35:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}离我只有一次忏悔的距离\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}One confession away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.67,0:36:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿兹班铁\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Azbantium.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.22,0:36:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比钻石硬四百倍\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}400 times harder than diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.80,0:36:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}厚二十尺\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}20 feet thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.44,0:36:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唯一的出口\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.20,0:36:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鸟儿\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.83,0:36:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是那个时候 我想起来了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's when I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.12,0:36:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远都是那个时候\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Always then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.67,0:36:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每次都是同一个时刻\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Always…then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.96,0:36:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远都是那个确切的瞬间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Always EXACTLY then!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.98,0:36:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能继续下去了 克拉拉 我做不到\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can't keep doing this, Clara! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.31,0:36:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么总是我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Why is it always me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.20,0:36:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么永远轮不到别人\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Why is it never anybody else's turn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.72,0:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}怎样才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.46,0:36:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}赢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.18,0:37:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就不能输一次吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Can't I just lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.96,0:37:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就这一次\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Just this once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.84,0:37:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}简单 会很简单\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Easy. It would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.13,0:37:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超级简单\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It would be SO easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.59,0:37:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只需要告诉他们\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Just tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.69,0:37:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要告诉想知道的人关于"混血"的一切\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Just tell them, whoever wants to know, all about the Hybrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.52,0:37:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能继续下去了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can't keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.08,0:37:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做不到\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.11,0:37:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能总是这样选择\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can't always do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.75,0:37:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这不公平\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.27,0:37:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉拉 这太不公平了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Clara, it's just not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.06,0:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为什么不能输\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Why can't I just lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.53,0:37:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}不
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.36,0:37:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我记得 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But I can remember, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.19,0:37:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不懂\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.80,0:37:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我全都记得\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I can remember it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.24,0:37:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每一次\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.29,0:38:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但你还是走了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And you'll still be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.39,0:38:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管我做什么\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Whatever I do…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.75,0:38:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你永远不会再回来了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You still won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.73,0:38:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}博士\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.21,0:38:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是只有你一个人失去过某人\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}You are not the only person who ever lost someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.90,0:38:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是所有人都会经历的事\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's the story of everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.33,0:38:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克服它\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打败它\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.16,0:38:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冲破枷锁\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Break free.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.74,0:38:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}博士 是时候了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Doctor, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.72,0:38:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站起来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Get up, off your arse…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.50,0:38:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去赢吧\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And win!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.56,0:39:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又见面了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Hello again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.26,0:39:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会再有忏悔了 抱歉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}No more confessions, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我会告诉你…真相\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But I will tell you…the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.55,0:39:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混血生物是个非常危险的秘密\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The Hybrid is a very dangerous secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.98,0:39:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个非常非常危险的秘密 必须守住\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}A very, very dangerous secret and it needs to be kept!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.52,0:39:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 我什么都不会告诉你\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, I'm telling you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.47,0:39:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有半点信息\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.48,0:39:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相反 我要做一件更激进的事\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Instead, I'm going to do something far worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.84,0:39:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要离开这里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm going to get out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.80,0:39:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找出当初是谁把我放到这里的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and find whoever put me here in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.29,0:40:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管他们准备做些什么 我都会阻止\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and whatever they're trying to do, I'm going to…stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.17,0:40:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这也许会花费一点时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}But it might take me a little while,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.64,0:40:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以你想不想听我讲个故事\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}so do you want me to tell you a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.79,0:40:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}格林兄弟 有趣的两个家伙\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The Brothers Grimm, lovely fellas…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.41,0:40:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们加入过同一个飞镖队\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}They're on my darts team.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.46,0:40:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}据他们说\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}According to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.25,0:40:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曾经有一位皇帝\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}there's this emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.56,0:40:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他问一位牧童\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and he asks this shepherd's boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.02,0:40:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}"永恒一共有多少秒"\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"How many seconds in eternity?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.86,0:41:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人们总是轻看时间领主\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}People always get it wrong with Time Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.57,0:41:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们命硬得很\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}We take forever to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.86,0:41:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即便我们伤重到无法重生\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Even if we're too injured to regenerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.53,0:41:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身体里的每一个细胞也会不断努力\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}every cell in our bodies keeps trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.17,0:41:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真正的死亡\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Dying properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.21,0:41:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可能需要好几天\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}can take days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.23,0:41:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是为什么我们喜欢在同族人身边死去\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That's why we like to die among our own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.32,0:41:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们知道不要提前下葬\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}They know not to bury us early.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.59,0:42:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想 以我现在的状态\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I think, in my current condition…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.27,0:42:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可能需要大约一天半的时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It'll take me about a day and a half
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.34,0:42:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来爬到塔顶\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}to reach the top of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.49,0:42:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.91,0:42:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我幸运的话\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If I'm lucky…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.63,0:42:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有一天半的时间\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I have a day and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.53,0:42:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须要这么做 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I have to do this, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.25,0:42:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是唯一的办法\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}It's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.73,0:42:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须坚强起来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I have to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.77,0:42:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我从一开始就应该知道的\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I should have known from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.13,0:42:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}显而易见\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.12,0:42:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的画像\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The portrait of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.74,0:42:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我噩梦里走出来的怪物\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}the creature from my own nightmares…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.69,0:42:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是为我私人订制的拷问室\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}This place is my own, bespoke torture chamber…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.55,0:43:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}专门针对我一个人\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Intended for me only,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.94,0:43:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至于水里的那些头骨\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and all those skulls in the water…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.07,0:43:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己的地狱里 怎么可能有别的囚犯\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}How could there be other prisoners…in my hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.97,0:43:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}答案显而易见\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The answer, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.61,0:43:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从未有过其他的囚犯\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}is there never were any other prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.15,0:43:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那些星星\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And the stars…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.59,0:43:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也没有错位\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}They weren't in the wrong place…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.28,0:43:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也没有进行时间旅行\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And I haven't time travelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.46,0:43:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是在这里\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I've just been here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.27,0:43:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}停留了很久很久\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}a very, very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.65,0:43:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每个房间都会重启\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Every room resets.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.64,0:44:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}记得我跟你说过的吗\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Remember I told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.58,0:44:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每个房间都会回到初始状态\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Every room reverts to its original condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.52,0:44:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逻辑上讲 传送器也是如此\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Logically, the teleporter should do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.59,0:44:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传送器 有趣的词\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"Teleporter" - fancy word.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.63,0:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实就像3D打印机\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Just like 3D printers, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.60,0:44:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只不过这个要先分解物质提取信息\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}except they break down living matter and information, 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.30,0:44:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后进行传送\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and transmit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.35,0:44:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你所需要做的 就是提供能量\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}All you have to do is add energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.65,0:44:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}房间已经重启\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}The room has reset,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.97,0:44:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回到了我刚来时的初始状态\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}returned to its original condition when I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.91,0:44:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这意味着有一个我的备份\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}That means there's a copy of me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.65,0:44:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还存在硬盘上面\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}still in the hard drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.26,0:44:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.85,0:44:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完好如新 和我最初到来时一样\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}exactly as I was…When I first got here…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.60,0:44:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在七千年前\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}7,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.22,0:44:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只需要一些能量\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}All I have to find is some energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.74,0:45:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要制造能量\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}And all you need for energy…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.32,0:45:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要找到燃料就行\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Is something to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.31,0:45:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}鸟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.44,0:45:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能这样继续多久 克拉拉\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}How long can I keep doing this, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.35,0:45:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燃烧旧我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Burning the old me…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.65,0:45:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来创造新我\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}To make a new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.78,0:46:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你以为她的死会使我变得脆弱\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If you think because she's dead, I am weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.02,0:46:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你对我知之甚少\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}then you understand very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.51,0:46:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你与她的死亡有关 而毫无惧意\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If you were any part of killing her and you're not afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.33,0:46:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你就是个一无所知的蠢货\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}then you understand nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.53,0:46:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以奉劝你一句 听好了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}So, for your own sake, understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.39,0:47:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是博士\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.16,0:47:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来找你了\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'm coming to find you,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.20,0:47:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我永远不会停止\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}and I will never, ever stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.42,0:47:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你绝对料不到下面这招\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}Because you won't see this coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.64,0:47:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我不知道\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}If I didn't know better,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.74,0:47:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会以为自己穿越到了七千年后的未来\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}I'd say I've travelled 7,000 years into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.22,0:47:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}"永恒一共有多少秒"\N{\b0\fs13\3c&H202020}"How many seconds in eternity?"
